---
import { Button, TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/sections/heros/HeroSection.astro';
import CtaCardSection from '../../components/sections/CtaCardSection.astro';
import CompareWiseNav from '../../components/compare-wise/CompareWiseNav.astro';

const seo = {
	title: 'Privacy Policy | Compare Wise',
	description:
		'Compare Wise privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.',
};
---

<Layout {seo}>
	<CompareWiseNav current="/compare-wise/privacy" />
	<HeroSection>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p>
				Last updated: June 22, 2026
			</p>
		</div>
		<div slot="btns-container">
			<Button href="/compare-wise" outlined>Back to Home</Button>
		</div>
		<picture slot="image-container">
			<img
				src="/assets/images/compare-wise/hero.png"
				alt="Compare Wise Privacy Policy"
				id="home-hero-image"
			/>
		</picture>
	</HeroSection>

	<TextSection narrow>
		<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
		<p>
			Compare Wise ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your
			privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose,
			and safeguard your information when you install and use our Shopify
			application.
		</p>
		<p>
			By installing Compare Wise from the Shopify App Store, you agree to the
			collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
		</p>

		<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
		<h3>Shopify Store Data</h3>
		<p>
			When you install Compare Wise, we access the following Shopify store
			data through the Shopify API:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Store name, URL, and contact information</li>
			<li>Shopify plan details (for billing compatibility)</li>
			<li>Theme information (to install the theme extension)</li>
			<li>Product data used in comparison tables (only when you choose to use it)</li>
		</ul>

		<h3>Comparison Table Content</h3>
		<p>
			We store the comparison table configurations, product data, and settings you
			create within the app. This data is stored on our servers solely for
			the purpose of rendering comparison tables on your storefront.
		</p>

		<h3>Analytics Data</h3>
		<p>
			For merchants on Pro and Enterprise plans, we collect table
			impression and engagement data to provide performance analytics. This
			data is anonymized and does not include personally identifiable
			information about your customers.
		</p>

		<h3>Account Information</h3>
		<p>
			We collect your email address and billing information through Shopify's
			secure billing system. We do not store credit card details directly.
		</p>

		<h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
		<p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Provide, operate, and maintain the Compare Wise application</li>
			<li>Render comparison tables on your Shopify storefront</li>
			<li>Process billing and subscription management</li>
			<li>Provide customer support and respond to inquiries</li>
			<li>Improve the application based on usage patterns</li>
			<li>Send important updates about the application (you may opt out)</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
		<p>
			We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third
			parts. We may share information only in the following circumstances:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>Shopify:</strong> We interact with Shopify's API to provide
				our service. Your data is subject to Shopify's privacy policies as
				well.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may use third-party services
				for hosting, analytics, and payment processing. These providers have
				access only to perform their tasks on our behalf and are obligated
				not to disclose or use it for other purposes.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose your information
				if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by
				public authorities.
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
		<p>
			We retain your data for as long as your Compare Wise installation is
			active. When you uninstall the app, we delete your comparison table data and
			analytics within 30 days. Store account information is retained for
			legal and accounting purposes for up to 5 years.
		</p>

		<h2>6. Data Security</h2>
		<p>
			We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data,
			including:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Encryption of data in transit (TLS/SSL)</li>
			<li>Encryption of stored data at rest</li>
			<li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
			<li>Access controls and authentication for all internal systems</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
		<p>You have the right to:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Access the personal data we hold about your store</li>
			<li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
			<li>Request deletion of your data</li>
			<li>Export your comparison table configurations in a portable format</li>
			<li>Object to processing of your data for certain purposes</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			To exercise any of these rights, contact us at
			<a href="mailto:miprio101@gmail.com">miprio101@gmail.com</a>.
		</p>

		<h2>8. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
		<p>
			Compare Wise uses minimal cookies necessary for the app's functionality
			within the Shopify admin. We do not use third-party tracking cookies
			on your storefront. Table impressions are tracked server-side and do
			not rely on browser cookies.
		</p>

		<h2>9. International Data Transfers</h2>
		<p>
			Your data may be processed in countries other than your own. We ensure
			that appropriate safeguards are in place for international data
			transfers, including standard contractual clauses where required by
			applicable law.
		</p>

		<h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
		<p>
			Compare Wise is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 18.
			We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
		</p>

		<h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
		<p>
			We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify
			you of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page and
			updating the "Last updated" date. Continued use of the app after
			changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
		</p>

		<h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
		<p>
			If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Email: <a href="mailto:miprio101@gmail.com">miprio101@gmail.com</a></li>
			<li>Website: <a href="https://frostmango.com">Frostmango</a></li>
		</ul>
	</TextSection>

	<CtaCardSection
		background="var(--theme-surface-2)"
		color="var(--theme-on-surface-2)"
	>
		<h2>Questions about your privacy?</h2>
		<p>
			We are here to help. Reach out to us anytime.
		</p>
		<Button href="mailto:miprio101@gmail.com">Contact Us</Button>
	</CtaCardSection>
</Layout>
